'''A Thousand Bones''' is a book written by [[P. J. Parrish]]<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.in/books?id=vkFbQ6BrQtcC&source=gbs_navlinks_s|title=A Thousand Bones|last=Parrish|first=P. J.|date=2007-06-26|publisher=Simon and Schuster|isbn=9781416559573|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.pjparrish.com/a-thousand-bones.php|title=Author P.J. Parrish|last=www.xuni.com|website=www.pjparrish.com|language=en-US|access-date=2017-03-25}}</ref> and published by [[Pocket Books]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.publishersweekly.com/978-1-4165-2587-5|title=Fiction Book Review: A Thousand Bones by P. J. Parrish, Author . Pocket $7.99 (470p) ISBN 978-1-4165-2587-5|work=PublishersWeekly.com|access-date=2017-03-25|language=en}}</ref> (owned by [[Simon & Schuster]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.simonandschuster.com/books/A-Thousand-Bones/P-J-Parrish/9781416525875|title=A Thousand Bones {{!}} Book by P. J. Parrish {{!}} Official Publisher Page|last=|first=|date=|website=Simon & Schuster|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref>) on 1 January 2007, which later went on to win the [[Anthony Award]] for Best Paperback Original in 2008.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bouchercon.com/anthony-awards/winners-and-nominees/2000s/|title=Winners and Nominees 2000s|date=2015-09-22|work=Bouchercon|access-date=2017-03-25|language=en}}</ref>
